{"tid":1843321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TOS-1噴火坦克24發地獄火　7秒連射毀掉小村莊","createTime":"2020-01-26T07:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T11:29:05.000Z","uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7ed54edd556ea8e92e759d711c4c797f758b830c","tid":1843321,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:02:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M36c5V2nD1g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DM36c5V2nD1g&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGegRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=f9864980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M36c5V2nD1g</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NXYqpM6W_Xs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNXYqpM6W_Xs&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGegRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=7eaaa357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NXYqpM6W_Xs</a><br />\nTOS-1是一款蘇聯開發的多管火箭炮，發射出的溫壓火箭會先將易燃液體散布在空氣中，然後瞬間點燃產生強大火焰，因此被俗稱為「噴火坦克」。原型射程為3.5公里，後來升級TOS-1A將射程突破到6公里，威脅能力大幅增高，只要全部24管發射，7秒就能直接摧毀一座小村莊。<br />\n<br />\n▲▼TOS-1火箭炮。（圖／翻攝自俄羅斯國防部）<br />\n<br />\n根據《衛星通訊社》（Sputnik）報導，這種短程多管火箭炮的概念始於70年代，到了80年代初鄂木斯克運輸工具製造廠研發成型，以T-72坦克底盤為基礎，上層裝設220毫米30管火箭炮，於1988年正式服役，首次亮相就在蘇聯對阿富汗的戰爭當中。<br />\n<br />\n▲▼TOS-1火箭炮。（圖／翻攝自俄羅斯國防部）<br />\n<br />\n升級版TOS-1A型變更為24管火箭砲，重量45噸、長度9.5公尺、寬3.6公尺、高度約2.2公尺，全車共有3名人員，透過雷射測距儀器與光學瞄準器完成瞄準，只要把發射器固定在正確的角度，操作員只要按下按鈕就能以每秒2發的速度射擊。研發團隊的首席設計師弗拉基米爾（Vladimir Medvedev）表示，原型的射程為3.5公里，後來升級版本突破到6公里，威脅能力大幅增高，發射出去的導彈會以陡峭拋物線飛行，幾乎會命中目標的正上方。<br />\n<br />\n▲▼TOS-1火箭炮。（圖／翻攝自俄羅斯國防部）<br />\n<br />\nTOS-1A型使用的彈藥是溫壓火箭，擊中目標後會先散布易燃液體在空氣中，隨後瞬間點燃產生毀滅性的爆炸，不僅衝擊波強大，燃燒時間持續比一般彈藥更長，可瞬間摧毀一座小村莊，巨大火團也有可怕的震懾力。除此之外，爆炸後會瞬間消耗區域間的氧氣，造成短暫真空狀態，使得躲藏在洞穴或掩體的敵人窒息死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: TOS-1噴火坦克24發地獄火 7秒連射毀掉小村莊 | ETtoday軍武 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180215/1107103.htm#ixzz6C7M2t1Br\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180215%2F1107103.htm%23ixzz6C7M2t1Br&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGegRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=12ec2494\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180215/1107103.htm#ixzz6C7M2t1Br</a><br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"5872033f104920e5852308f3276e402a194b8758","tid":1843321,"uid":264965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:03:42.000Z","msg":"武漢方案"},{"pid":"82b3718fe88cbbd7a3a9b051eeac966b8b6fe0f1","tid":1843321,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:09:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-07/04/35191.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2019-07%2F04%2F35191.html&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGegRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=751f440b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-07/04/35191.html</a><br />\n<br />\n甘若水：「遠火王者」PHL03型火箭炮嘯傲青藏高原<br />\n2019-07-04<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bdgoTw3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbdgoTw3.jpg&h=46de745d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸有更強的PHL03型火箭炮(自稱)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">果然棋王早有準備</span>"},{"pid":"a4ff0620b8706dfe3c765f48da4e0a21266809d7","tid":1843321,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"可以幫武漢進行高溫消毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558f5fe786cc457a1eb6300e6b27450dcd9fa286","tid":1843321,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsXzfNk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgsXzfNk.gif&h=b39036f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n空投"},{"pid":"86deb8b78782945783413203656d67a2eb6f16d5","t